# Intuition
The problem of determining whether one string is an interleaving of two others can be approached using dynamic programming. The core intuition lies in breaking down the problem into smaller subproblems. Essentially, we want to determine if the characters from both strings, s1 and s2, can be interwoven to create the target string s3. We aim to build a dynamic programming matrix that stores the state of the interleaving at different points, helping us track the possibilities.

# Solution Video

### Please subscribe to my channel from here. I have 247 videos as of August 25th.

**■ Subscribe URL**
http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9RMNwYTL3SXCP6ShLWVFww?sub_confirmation=1

